@startuml
title Full System Sequence Diagram - Building Maintenance ERP

actor "Admin/Resident" as User
participant "React Frontend" as UI
participant "Spring Security / JWT" as Auth
participant "Spring Boot Controller" as API
participant "Service Layer" as Service
participant "Database (MySQL)" as DB
participant "System Scheduler" as Robot
participant "External Libs (iText/POI)" as Libs

== 1. Authentication & Setup ==
User -> UI: Enter Credentials
UI -> Auth: POST /login
Auth -> DB: Validate User
DB --> Auth: User Roles (ADMIN/USER)
Auth --> UI: Return JWT Token
UI -> UI: Store Token & UserID

== 2. Admin: Flat & User Management ==
User -> UI: Add Flat / Assign Resident
UI -> API: PUT /api/flats/assign/{id}
API -> Service: assignUserToFlat()
Service -> DB: Update Flat Status & OwnerID
DB --> UI: Success Response

== 3. Billing Logic (Dual Path) ==
alt #LightBlue Manual Generation (Admin)
    User -> UI: Click "Generate Bills"
    UI -> API: POST /api/finance/generate
else #Lavender Auto-Billing (System)
    Robot -> Service: @Scheduled (1st of Month)
    Service -> DB: Check SystemSettings Toggle
end
Service -> DB: Fetch All Flats & Residents
Service -> Service: Calculate Amount
Service -> DB: Save MaintenanceBills (Status: PENDING)
DB --> UI: Notification: "Bills Generated"

== 4. Resident: Payment & Receipts ==
User -> UI: View Bills -> Click "Pay Now"
UI -> API: PUT /api/finance/bills/{id}/pay
API -> Service: processPayment()
Service -> DB: Update Status to "PAID"
Service -> DB: Update Master Balance (Credit)
DB --> UI: Payment Success
User -> UI: Click "Download Receipt"
UI -> API: GET /api/finance/bills/{id}/download
API -> Libs: iText: generatePDF()
Libs --> UI: Return PDF Blob
UI -> User: Download Receipt.pdf

== 5. Admin: Expenses & Transparency ==
User -> UI: Add Expense (Repairs/Salaries)
UI -> API: POST /api/finance/expenses
API -> Service: recordExpense()
Service -> DB: Update Master Balance (Debit)
DB --> UI: Balance Sheet Updated
User -> UI: View Balance Sheet (Total Income vs Expense)

== 6. Directory & Export ==
User -> UI: Search Resident Directory
UI -> API: GET /api/flats/directory
API -> DB: Fetch Joined Flat-User Data
DB --> UI: Return List
User -> UI: Click "Export Excel"
UI -> API: GET /api/flats/export/excel
API -> Libs: Apache POI: buildExcel()
Libs --> UI: Return .xlsx file
UI -> User: Download Directory.xlsx

@enduml